name: TuscaloosaVegan

skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: tuscaloosa vegan
des: List of vegetarian and vegan restaurant options in Tuscaloosa. Includes addresses, phone number, and brief descriptions which can be heard from Alexa, and read in the companion Alexa app. To enable, say "Alexa, enable Tuscaloosa Vegan." Then to use, simply say, "Alexa, ask Tuscaloosa Vegan for a fact."
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
